msgid ""
"Togo Rail — Relier le Togo, connecter l’Afrique de l’Ouest. Fret "
"ferroviaire, transport de voyageurs et logistique intégrée."
msgstr ""
"Togo Rail — Connecting Togo, powering West Africa. Rail freight, passenger "
"transport and integrated logistics."

msgid "À propos"
msgstr "About"

msgid "À propos de Togo Rail"
msgstr "About Togo Rail"

msgid "L’avenir du rail"
msgstr "The future of rail"

msgid "commence ici."
msgstr "starts here."

msgid ""
"Depuis notre création, nous plaçons la fiabilité, la sécurité et la "
"durabilité au cœur de chaque kilomètre de voie que nous construisons."
msgstr ""
"Since day one, we have put reliability, safety and sustainability at the "
"heart of every kilometre of track we build."

msgid "Mission"
msgstr "Mission"

msgid ""
"Connecter les personnes et les marchandises grâce à une infrastructure "
"ferroviaire de classe mondiale."
msgstr ""
"Connecting people and goods through world-class railway infrastructure."

msgid "Vision"
msgstr "Vision"

msgid "Devenir le corridor logistique de référence de l’Afrique de l’Ouest."
msgstr "To become West Africa's leading logistics corridor."

msgid "Valeurs"
msgstr "Values"

msgid "Excellence, sécurité, durabilité et engagement envers les communautés."
msgstr "Excellence, safety, sustainability and commitment to communities."

msgid "Notre parcours"
msgstr "Our journey"

msgid "Une progression"
msgstr "Steady"

msgid "constante."
msgstr "progress."

