msgstr "Send message"

msgid "Mobilité ferroviaire premium"
msgstr "Premium rail mobility"

msgid "Togo Rail · Infrastructure de nouvelle génération"
msgstr "Togo Rail · Next-generation infrastructure"

msgid "Relier le Togo,"
msgstr "Connecting Togo,"

msgid "propulser l’Afrique."
msgstr "powering Africa."

msgid ""
"Fret ferroviaire, transport de voyageurs et logistique intégrée. Une "
"infrastructure fiable, durable et intelligente au cœur de l’Afrique de "
"l’Ouest."
msgstr ""
"Rail freight, passenger transport and integrated logistics. Reliable, "
"sustainable and intelligent infrastructure at the heart of West Africa."

msgid "Découvrir nos services"
msgstr "Explore our services"

msgid "Nous contacter"
msgstr "Get in touch"

msgid "Défiler"
msgstr "Scroll"

msgid "Ils nous font confiance"
msgstr "Trusted by"

msgid "Nos expertises"
msgstr "Our expertise"

msgid "Des solutions ferroviaires"
msgstr "End-to-end railway"

msgid "de bout en bout."
msgstr "solutions."

msgid "Tous les services →"
msgstr "All services →"

msgid "En savoir plus"
msgstr "Learn more"

msgid "Le contenu sera bientôt disponible."
msgstr "Content will be available soon."

msgid "Notre raison d’être"
msgstr "Our purpose"

msgid "Nous construisons l’épine dorsale"
msgstr "We are building the backbone"

msgid "de la mobilité togolaise."
msgstr "of Togolese mobility."

msgid ""
"Togo Rail conçoit et opère des infrastructures ferroviaires modernes qui "
"accélèrent le commerce, rapprochent les territoires et réduisent l’empreinte "
"carbone des transports."
msgstr ""
"Togo Rail designs and operates modern railway infrastructure that "
"accelerates trade, brings regions closer together and reduces the carbon "
"footprint of transport."

msgid ""
"Offrir une mobilité fiable, sûre et durable à chaque citoyen et entreprise."
msgstr ""
"To deliver reliable, safe and sustainable mobility to every citizen and "
"business."

msgid "Faire du Togo un hub logistique majeur de l’Afrique de l’Ouest."
msgstr "To make Togo a major logistics hub in West Africa."

msgid "Prêt à faire avancer votre projet logistique ?"
msgstr "Ready to move your logistics project forward?"

msgid ""
"Parlons de vos besoins en transport et infrastructure. Notre équipe vous "
"répond sous 24h."
msgstr ""
"Let's discuss your transport and infrastructure needs. Our team replies "
"within 24 hours."

msgid "Demander un devis"
msgstr "Request a quote"

msgid "Nos services"
msgstr "Our services"

msgid "Une expertise"
msgstr "Complete railway"

msgid "ferroviaire complète."
msgstr "expertise."

msgid ""
"Du fret longue distance à la logistique du dernier kilomètre, nous couvrons "
"toute la chaîne de valeur du transport ferroviaire."
msgstr ""
"From long-haul freight to last-mile logistics, we cover the entire railway "
"transport value chain."

msgid "Un besoin spécifique ?"
msgstr "A specific need?"

msgid "Construisons ensemble une solution logistique sur mesure."
msgstr "Let's build a tailor-made logistics solution together."

